{"tid":2229702,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"300呎公屋大改造變4房1廳 雙趟門睡房一分為二各有空間","createTime":"2020-10-04T14:40:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T02:28:09.000Z","uid":66271,"like":8,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"70c37e51337bf0c1549d62b9bccc1e2fe83ae059","tid":2229702,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:40:04.000Z","msg":"香港寸金尺土，未必每個人都可擁有獨立的房間。有室內設計公司為滿足一家五口「各有空間」的要求，將一個300呎公屋單位大改造，變成「4房1廳」，透過雙趟門設計，把一個空間分成兩間「睡房」。<br />\n<br />\n室內設計公司「Honest Design」早前分享一個特色單位翻新，位於大埔太和邨亨和樓，面積約300呎，一家五口同住。屋主表示除了要有廁所、廚房之外，亦希望有4個獨立房間，故設計師用盡每一吋空間，將單位改造成「4房1廳」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2760000/2760782/2_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2760000%2F2760782%2F2_600.jpg&h=61d85892&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n房間一分二 分兩個通道出入<br />\n<br />\n由於屋主希望子女能有獨立空間，又不想他們睡「碌架房」，設計師在近大門位置間出房間，並利用白色「雙趟門」設計，將空間一分為二，設兩個入口，一個以樓梯上落，另一個則以床尾位置出入，變成兩個「獨立睡房」，<br />\n<br />\n將趟門拉到左邊：會見到連接「上層房」的黑色小樓梯；<br />\n當趟門拉到右邊：可從床尾進入「下層房」。<br />\n房間格局與膠囊旅館相似，惟設計師澄清靈感來源並非來自膠囊旅館，「個單位要住咁多人，就要搵方法去解決」。他續指，「雙趟門」可讓他們於自己的獨立通道出入，將空間分間為上下兩層，各自可擁有私人空間。雖然房間如同膠囊旅館般大小，但有獨立燈光，不會影響對方，<br />\n<br />\n「仔女見到自己細小的房間，也明白空間有限，能有一個獨立空間已心滿意足。」<br />\n設計師除了在子女房的下層床作地台設計，又在大門的另一側設置黑色儲物櫃，作為單位的主要儲物空間。而子女房的後方，則單位的第三間房，為家中長者的睡房，房門對出是客廳。<br />\n<br />\n第一、二房間︰<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2760000/2760782/20200923public10_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2760000%2F2760782%2F20200923public10_600.jpg&h=e1bc72da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2760000/2760782/20200923public08_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2760000%2F2760782%2F20200923public08_600.jpg&h=3a26dda1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2760000/2760782/20200923public09_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2760000%2F2760782%2F20200923public09_600.jpg&h=a18391ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第三間房︰<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2760000/2760782/20200923public15_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2760000%2F2760782%2F20200923public15_600.jpg&h=791f05ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第四間房：<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2760000/2760782/20200923public04_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2760000%2F2760782%2F20200923public04_600.jpg&h=3f2c9020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n客廳：靠燈飾改善採光不足<br />\n<br />\n由於單位面積有限，設計師指沒有特別將客飯廳作區間，在客廳位置增加一面灰色鏡面特色牆，藉此增加空間感，為原本以單一白色牆為主的客廳注入型格感覺。由於客飯廳屬「黑廳」設計，採光度不足，故透過假天花燈槽照亮整個空間，確保光線柔和之餘，又可增加樓底空間感。<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2760000/2760782/20200923public16_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2760000%2F2760782%2F20200923public16_600.jpg&h=0e81d73a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n浴室乾濕分離 淋浴不怕弄濕坐廁<br />\n<br />\n設計師表示，一般公屋單位浴室空間有限，難以做到乾濕分離，導致沖涼淋浴時往往弄濕坐廁，今次設計師拆走原本的牆身再重建，「偷」更多位加大廁所空間，將淋浴位置與馬桶分隔開。<br />\n<br />\n公屋單位原裝修都是採用明喉，屋主略縑不夠美觀，希望可以遮蓋喚位。設計師指，單位廁所及廚房牆身之間有不少貫穿上下層的明喉，需要重新規劃水喉路徑，最後做到私樓的效果，屋主非常滿意。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2760000/2760782/20200923public01_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2760000%2F2760782%2F20200923public01_600.jpg&h=a78fe730&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2760000/2760782/20200923public02_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2760000%2F2760782%2F20200923public02_600.jpg&h=d01135c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2760000/2760782/20200923public13_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2760000%2F2760782%2F20200923public13_600.jpg&h=9622a02a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3ee70dd0a9e8136962295d184b9ca7dba00d7ec","tid":2229702,"uid":197163,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:40:56.000Z","msg":"公屋，租約黎，裝修咁靚做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea5860a367f723c0e034386b7f1b8859067128be","tid":2229702,"uid":71508,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:47:48.000Z","msg":"得個toilet叫ok"},{"pid":"d16c47986b5789acd46ba398281f498228186b1f","tid":2229702,"uid":81651,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:50:12.000Z","msg":"咁樣叫房？太空艙適合啲"},{"pid":"a4d73b06800553bfc926adccfb4d254000ca5e33","tid":2229702,"uid":35623,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"d3ee70dd0a9e8136962295d184b9ca7dba00d7ec","tid":2229702,"uid":197163,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:40:56.000Z","msg":"公屋，租約黎，裝修咁靚做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:53:38.000Z","msg":"太和 九成買左"},{"pid":"f723ef4bc20c93f1e72538121d9fbfa4face1d4e","tid":2229702,"uid":30379,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:04:28.000Z","msg":"第三間房睇唔明,個廁所幾靚"},{"pid":"e0bf7668797462f433c50b35ca7d1965dc49434d","tid":2229702,"uid":987,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:09:42.000Z","msg":"廁所幾靚"},{"pid":"35a437d611e30abb35d5be5fd52b95a5da6fd14d","tid":2229702,"uid":49574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:12:15.000Z","msg":"廁所廚房幾好呀"},{"pid":"3402322837b72e77d7abfe600c8bbb3a8aa97682","tid":2229702,"uid":24570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:18:09.000Z","msg":"又幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f349804c2ca3f42fbf7daea0f5c46daa7b4ac3c5","tid":2229702,"uid":16676,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:18:48.000Z","msg":"太空倉上下格仲要打通無私隱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪同碌架床無分別, 下面果個係樓梯底捐入去就得<br />\n洗乜專登開床尾度門入<br />\n一開床尾度門<br />\n上格床會知道, 同時又係比人睇晒, <br />\n一樣係無神神打緊飛機有人突然開門既情景一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">不如一齊係樓梯捐入去.... 唔使係床尾爬上床</span></strong><br />\n咁洗乜兩面趟門.... 多撚餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分黎做乜....... 好無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349335bd0793d615a53767b16730c894fe787255","tid":2229702,"uid":348821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:22:02.000Z","msg":"見到咁逼咁窄又唔通風就覺得抖唔到氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ffb81919c8d7ba520f51d2bcd035d02089e54a","tid":2229702,"uid":106408,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:26:41.000Z","msg":"其實真係唔錯"},{"pid":"6e75f6d362a37bbd0d4ac0f3de1775c2efe04099","tid":2229702,"uid":16676,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:27:13.000Z","msg":"果間所謂房..... 跟本個角位係偷黎比沖涼位用<br />\n與其係咁.... 情願無沖涼花灑位<br />\n比返正正經經間房用好過.... 反正沖涼耐極都係30mins... <br />\n每日訓覺隨時8hrs up<br />\n反而為左沖涼犧牲左訓覺既地方<br />\n呢個設計師已經唔合格....... 無料+九流到爆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb61e3308d4fe12d7c88147945edbf64277ae760","tid":2229702,"uid":63303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d3ee70dd0a9e8136962295d184b9ca7dba00d7ec","tid":2229702,"uid":197163,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T14:40:56.000Z","msg":"公屋，租約黎，裝修咁靚做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:30:21.000Z","msg":"一住就十幾廿年，整好啲舒服自己"},{"pid":"93994f4329ad0688235253fe05f2c51610d0a71c","tid":2229702,"uid":260113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:38:14.000Z","msg":"仲差過膠囊旅館..."},{"pid":"c3572fa07ed636a2c5c2f373e869e0bb320e75a1","tid":2229702,"uid":13343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:49:20.000Z","msg":"到底一張床貼住三邊都係牆係咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n地方細得兩邊落床都明<br />\n<br />\n但屌你三邊都係牆仲衰撚過監倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249a2e6f4540688f20b9e8cb1be4aa674d2d21b9","tid":2229702,"uid":3179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:13:55.000Z","msg":"個抽油煙機....."},{"pid":"a54aebd8d15f078a23f0736925e786986e1d2c65","tid":2229702,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:17:34.000Z","msg":"幾靚"},{"pid":"290422a822216d306b3c848d82af2203c44eb805","tid":2229702,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:35:25.000Z","msg":"邊度呀 幫手report 下漏水"},{"pid":"a72e96dd4974dbf9a55c79d9184a9237a97025da","tid":2229702,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:48:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad69986e1dbefda7c9ae78031a07f160be706efc","tid":2229702,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a72e96dd4974dbf9a55c79d9184a9237a97025da","tid":2229702,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3572fa07ed636a2c5c2f373e869e0bb320e75a1","tid":2229702,"uid":13343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:49:20.000Z","msg":"到底一張床貼住三邊都係牆係咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n地方細得兩邊落床都明<br />\n<br />\n但屌你三邊都係牆仲衰撚過監倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:48:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T17:03:01.000Z","msg":"劏房無計<br />\n但佢嗰個係屋企嚟<br />\n咁樣真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304180f5c420e990da72373b4a95eb92c263d6fe","tid":2229702,"uid":69013,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T23:42:17.000Z","msg":"300尺4間房太誇張啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然第1/2房當一間。 <br />\n第三間係唔係即係瞓廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"24cf9a238eea46b015b4abe3abdbb1e4e629afd5","tid":2229702,"uid":22325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T00:06:19.000Z","msg":"次次裝修post都比連登仔𨳒到一文不值<br />\n好想睇下眾連登仔嘅屋企有幾靚<br />\n留名等J連登仔屋企，幾時有人post自己屋企嘅靚裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" cla